or manmade. The Novel Delivery Technology for Medical Countermeasures program will develop minimally invasive MCM
delivery systems, in which any therapeutic can be quickly formulated and administered to treat or prevent any disease. Developing
novel delivery platforms will maintain warfighter health and readiness and enable rapid response to existing and novel biothreats.

