Title: Embedded Entrepreneurship Initiative (EEI)                                                                                             -             -       25.000
Description: EEI pairs top technical talent from DARPA programs with experienced business leaders to accelerate the transition
of breakthrough technologies to market. The program provides hands-on go-to-market support, equipping teams with the tools,
expertise, and strategies needed to succeed in both government and commercial sectors. By fostering strong commercialization
