- Complete development of initial Arbitrary Waveform and advanced signal processing capability (CX 7.0).
FY 2026 Plans:
- Integrate and test initial Arbitrary Waveform and advanced signal processing capability for the AN/TPY-2 CX 7.0 baseline.
- Initiate AN/TPY-2 Electronic Protection development in support of the Golden Dome for America architecture.
