5 assets, which consist of Arrow-2 and Arrow-3 missiles, launchers, GPs and SGP, Citron Tree BMC, Hazelnut Tree LCCs,
ABEWS, and Lego Shield. Development continues for the Sharp Eye sensor suite, Arrow-4 interceptor and Pine Woods Radar for
future AWS Blocks. Continue proven Interoperability with U.S. Assets and enhancements to existing AWS System Components.

Specific and/or unique planned accomplishments to each FY are as follows:

