The fiscal year (FY) 2026 request for Ballistic Missile Defense (BMD) Enabling Programs includes $179.7 million of discretionary and $81.0 million of mandatory
(reconciliation) for a total of $260.7 million. The mandatory (reconciliation) funds provide for the initiation of Golden Dome for America requirements, including
