FY 2025 Plans:
- Continue undersea platform data fusion integration into USW-DSS Build 3 FCR 3 to include Integrated
Broadcast Service (IBS), Thresher, Integrated Undersea Surveillance System (IUSS), and Maritime Targeting
Cell-Afloat (MTC-A).
- Improve zonal software architecture to enhance data security of multi-source data fusion. This will allow for
increased data-sharing between TUSW Commanders and allied partners.
- Develop and improve system virtualization and web-based architecture to enhance supportability,
maintainability, and increase user access without growing the hardware footprint.
- Develop and test secure container-based architecture to improve system maintainability and supportability.



