- Increased manual search sectors: Expands the minimum allowable freeform sectors, increasing manual radar doctrine search
capability to enhance warfighter planning and radar detection.
- L201a/L202 design cases: Adds initial capability against evolving ballistic missile threats.
- SM-3 Block IB Enhanced Aegis Data Link: Provides interface update between AN/SPY-1 Radar and SM-3 Block IB missiles.
